1.01	Murder_of_Fernando_Mart%C3%AD	Murder of Fernando Martí	Fernando Martí Haik (c. 1994–2008) was the 14-year-old son of a wealthy sporting goods chain owner Alejandro Marti, whose kidnapping and murder caused a national outrage in Mexico, with some hoping that involvement of such a wealthy family might help draw attention to the issue. The murder was noticeable for its implication of mid-level law enforcement officials in Mexico City.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/e/ee/Mart%C3%AD_funeral.jpg/220px-Mart%C3%AD_funeral.jpg
